00064 #define Cl_EOF          -1      /* end of file */

00079 typedef struct _Cl_List
00080 {
00081   char *file;                   /* file name */
00082   int line;                     /* line number */
00083   int column;                   /* column position */
00084   short type;                   /* token type */

00086   union
00087   {
00088     C_Integer scalar;           /* scalar value */
00089     C_Double real;              /* floating point value */
00090     struct _Cl_List *child;     /* child list */
00091   }
00092   value;
00093   struct _Cl_List *sibling;     /* sibling */
00094 }
00095 _Cl_List, *Cl_List;
